  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Fashion Advisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and welcome customers as they enter the store, creating a friendly and inviting atmosphere.</li><li>Assist customers in finding the ideal products that suit their preferences and needs.</li><li>Provide in-depth product knowledge and educate customers on the latest fashion trends, features, and unique selling points of our company products.</li><li>Process sales transactions accurately and efficiently, handling cash, credit cards, and other payment methods.</li><li>Meet and exceed individual and team sales targets while maintaining high levels of customer satisfaction.</li><li>Handle customer inquiries, complaints, and returns in a professional and courteous manner.</li><li>Assist with housekeeping, inventory management, and conducting regular stock checks.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in retail sales, preferably in the fashion industry or footwear segment.</li><li>Passion for fashion, footwear, and staying current with industry trends.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to engage and connect with customers.</li><li>Strong sales acumen and the ability to upsell products effectively.</li><li>Customer-focused approach with a positive attitude and a willingness to go the extra mile for customer satisfaction.</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and handle multiple tasks efficiently.</li></ul><p></p>",
